    public class GeoWaveFeatureSource
extends org.geotools.data.AbstractFeatureLocking
implements org.geotools.data.simple.SimpleFeatureSource
    This is directly used by GeoWave's GeoTools DataStore to get a GeoTools data reader or feature collection for a specific feature type (defined by a GeoWave FeatureDataAdapter). This uses EPSG:4326 as the default CRS.
